title: Estonia CPI Transportation
description: The transportation sub-index of the CPI basket in Estonia increased to 252.43 points in October of 2022 from 250.73 points in September of 2022. CPI Transportation in Estonia averaged 158.94 points from 1994 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 259.53 points in June of 2022 and a record low of 43 points in January of 1994. This page provides - Estonia Cpi Transportation- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics Estonia
